  <brief_title>Patient Satisfaction and Quality of Life Impact - PecFent®</brief_title>
  <acronym>Qualipec</acronym>
  <official_title>A French, Multicentre, Open-label, Observational Study to Assess Quality of Life and Satisfaction in Subjects Taking PecFent® for the Treatment of Breakthrough Cancer Pain (BTPc)</official_title>
